{"tid":587783,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人用過owncloud黎整database","createTime":"2018-03-10T16:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T02:31:45.000Z","uid":53533,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"86f5af0399bafc90c21b55ec9d5bab3e3e2decef","tid":587783,"uid":53533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T16:36:22.000Z","msg":"小弟新手近排學緊寫app 亦都係第一次用owncloud <br />\n有個問題唔係好識解決<br />\n<br />\n我用左owncloud整左個MySQL Database <br />\n都寫左個php 比個app去拎番data<br />\n<br />\n但個問題就係我試左好多次都拎唔到個php<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nUrl係點打先正確<br />\n有冇人用開owncloud可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0207838f1d1e4d781751d9bfa399654181cafc","tid":587783,"uid":33883,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:27:27.000Z","msg":"完全唔知你噏乜, ownCloud只係一嚿雲, 最多咪畀你用嚟儲下啲database files同sync上sync落啫, 照計唔會無啦啦提供個MySQL API畀你用, 佢更加唔係一個MySQL server, 都唔知你整個PHP嚟攞乜嘢?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n(最近想由ownCloud轉用Nextcloud, 避免出現vendor-lock困局!)"},{"pid":"886225dfd05c93ea64d7a4c7eaf43437d87f577f","tid":587783,"uid":79546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:42:59.000Z","msg":"Concept錯 <br />\nOwncloud只係synchronization上幫到手<br />\n冇可能就咁當MySQL server<br />\n更加冇可能就咁php做到data retrieval <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87dbc619fe1a2f5a06ee90a6676e5d25931fa6bf","tid":587783,"uid":60249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:44:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37b2570c60f9ed0b7ca5ee349e18d07bd9db47cb","tid":587783,"uid":60249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:46:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb8014a0d38ef6c45ea285104f81d0335006424b","tid":587783,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a0207838f1d1e4d781751d9bfa399654181cafc","tid":587783,"uid":33883,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:27:27.000Z","msg":"完全唔知你噏乜, ownCloud只係一嚿雲, 最多咪畀你用嚟儲下啲database files同sync上sync落啫, 照計唔會無啦啦提供個MySQL API畀你用, 佢更加唔係一個MySQL server, 都唔知你整個PHP嚟攞乜嘢?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n(最近想由ownCloud轉用Nextcloud, 避免出現vendor-lock困局!)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T18:22:39.000Z","msg":"Check真啲, 原來真係得, 要自膠一下! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://doc.owncloud.org/server/10.0/admin_manual/configuration/database/linux_database_configuration.html \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdoc.owncloud.org%2Fserver%2F10.0%2Fadmin_manual%2Fconfiguration%2Fdatabase%2Flinux_database_configuration.html%20&d=lFiEHTbThI6sZWFhNxqiYZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7f10ffbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://doc.owncloud.org/server/10.0/admin_manual/configuration/database/linux_database_configuration.html </a>"},{"pid":"d228e1bccb17372cc041660033dbdd2dbf51a78f","tid":587783,"uid":4284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:31:45.000Z","msg":"用firebase database玩下先啦"}]}